  "body": "logger module should introduce ILoggingOptions and logging description (cli configuration).\nOnly option I can think of is \"loggingLevels\" which should contain somekind of mapping module: loggingLevel. Exmp. chain=debug, network=trace, database=warn.\nILoggingOptions should be added to BeaconNode options.\nLogger should also be able to set prefix and each module should initialize own logger adn set prefix.\nFor example. Chain module would initialize logger with prefix `[CHAIN]` and appropriate loggin level from config and it's log output should be:\n`[CHAIN] Beacon chain initialized`\n",
